OL,4,Cbiggest prize in Las Vegas
OL,6,FA bodybuilder and personal trainer who
OL,7,Fwon one of the biggest prizes in the
OL,8,Fworld of drug-free bodybuilding says
OL,9,Fhe 'never thought he'd win such a good
OL,10,Fshow.'
OL,12,FBen Lloyd, 40, from Accrington, became
OL,13,Fthe first British bodybuilder to be
OL,14,Fcrowned champion at the Natural
OL,15,FOlympia in Las Vegas, taking home a
OL,16,F#10,000 prize.
OL,18,FSporting success runs in his family,
OL,19,Fas his dad is the famous former
OL,20,FLancashire and England cricketer
OL,21,Fturned commentator David Lloyd.
