OL,6,FBut unlike his dad, Ben spends his
OL,7,Fdays in the gym rather than the
OL,8,Fcricket pitch, where he has found his
OL,9,Fstrengths lie.
OL,11,FSpeaking on his recent success, Ben
OL,12,Fsaid: "Never thought I'd win such a
OL,13,Fgood show. You go away just thinking
OL,14,FI'll get in the top five maybe.
OL,16,F"But to win requires a lot of luck as
OL,17,Fwell, because it's all judges
OL,18,Fopinions. To win is just an amazing
OL,19,Ffeeling."
