OL,3,CDrug-free bodybuilder wins sports'
OL,4,Cbiggest prize in Las Vegas
OL,6,FCompetitors in this competition are
OL,7,Fbanned from taking steroids or other
OL,8,Fperformance-enhancing drugs - and can
OL,9,Fbe punished with bans of up to four
OL,10,Fyears if they break the rules.
OL,12,F"I think it's a healthier way of doing
OL,13,Fit", Ben said, who is drug-free. "I
OL,14,Fthink anyone that is into bodybuilding
OL,15,Fshould go down the drug-free route
OL,16,Ffirst instead of going the other way.
