OL,6,F"It's a little bit harder, I think, in
OL,7,Fterms of the length of diets that you
OL,8,Fhave to do. That's what's required to
OL,9,Flose all the fat. You've just got to
OL,10,Fbe really consistent with a diet and
OL,11,Fnot slip up.
OL,13,F"It's a heck of a discipline to do it.
OL,14,FIt's a passion for all the
OL,15,Fbodybuilders, but the ambition and the
OL,16,Fdedication and the discipline is
OL,17,Fabsolutely paramount because you can't
OL,18,Fyou can't cut corners."
