OL,6,FBen's also a personal trainer and put
OL,7,Fhis dad through his paces. So, could
OL,8,Ffather and son one day compete
OL,9,Ftogether?
OL,11,F"It's all about genetics. I've got it
OL,12,Ffrom somewhere. I think they do it in
OL,13,Fover 70", Ben said.JHis dad responded:
OL,14,F"No not that again. When I turned 70
OL,15,Fhe said I'll get in the over 70s
OL,16,FWorld. No!"
