OL,6,FWhen he won the title, Ben wrote on
OL,7,Fsocial media: "Your new PNBA Pro
OL,8,FNatural Olympia Overall Champion! This
OL,9,Fis by far the greatest achievement of
OL,10,Fmy bodybuilding career so far and I'm
OL,11,Fcompletely lost for words.
OL,13,F"To win one of the best natural
OL,14,Fbodybuilding shows in the world
OL,15,Fagainst over 20 elite level pros is
OL,16,Fbeyond my wildest expectations. Thanks
OL,17,Fto everyone that has supported me."
